## Node name
-name beamclaw@127.0.0.1

## Cookie
-setcookie beamclaw_dev

## Heartbeat management; auto-restarts VM if it stops responding
## -heart

## Enable SMP automatically based on availability
+S auto

## Increase number of concurrent ports/sockets
+Q 65536

## Set the scheduler busy wait threshold
+sbwt none

## Set async threads
+A 32

## Crash dump location
-env ERL_CRASH_DUMP /tmp/beamclaw_erl_crash.dump
